CatDescriptText: An elderly shoe repairmen mending the sole of a woman's heel.  Behind him is a lathe set up with multiple brushes used for polishing shoes.  On the shelf above him are 'Cats Paw' replacement soles of various sizes and shapes.
TitMainTitle: Man wearing suspenders, holding hammer, in shoe repair workshop with tools on table and shelves with Cat's Paw boxes in background
